      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shallot halves</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges</strong> and <strong>chopped red pepper </strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-22 min or until the veg is tender and the red pepper is slightly charred – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
