    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>to a bowl with<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>fennel seeds</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix thoroughly until fully combined, divide into 5 per person and roll into meatballs – these are your <strong>pork meatballs</strong></p>",
