    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> and cook for an initial 4-5 min or until starting to brown all over</p>",
