    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once the veg is tender and slightly charred, add the <strong>roasted veg</strong> to the <strong>food processor</strong> with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!), your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[ 1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and smooth – this is your <strong>Greek cheese &</strong> <strong>red pepper sauce</strong></p>",
